            • [ - ] Turan - member since 22-Nov-13

              Oh and about the disallowed goal, it is valid and the assistant got that wrong but that is part of football, refs get things wrong every now and then. No need to go for witchhunt because we lost 2 points because of the mistake. There will be times we will get good calls and other times that we will get bad ones. On the long run the pro and against us calls even out. So don't listen to those that tell you they hate Real Madrid nor the ones that claim that refs help Real Madrid by awarding them more penalties. If one reviews all the penalties given in all the games, they will conclude that the mistakes are random and that the reason why big teams get more penalties are simply because they create more chances in the rival penalty box and therefore it is logical to get more penalties.
